{"tid":252180,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"jj插沙求救 砌完機搵唔到ssd裝win10","createTime":"2017-05-21T13:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T16:42:50.000Z","uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"059e8a869ff48345e5ff49061600f9d1a7d2b12c","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"今日幫舊機升級 換左做r5 1600<br />\n底板ausu b350-a<br />\nssd係intel 600p m.2個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家我搵唔到個ssd裝window10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa968a806130d6eb994133f70a883d09dfe8408e","tid":252180,"uid":84144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:49:20.000Z","msg":"cmos/bios de唔detect到隻硬碟？"},{"pid":"9d60ec23b06bf527b986dad5ddc1cfae871b677d","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cmos/bios de唔detect到隻硬碟？</blockquote><br />\ncmos我唔知咩黎 不過bios 搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0507f5f4fefa3ee9f195b537f96286dca97a96","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/215539_bc344860f7e2aac3a9e5785cf4f76bfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F215539_bc344860f7e2aac3a9e5785cf4f76bfe.jpg&h=78e107da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我個m.2 ssd係ssdpekkw256g7x1<br />\n我好似係我塊板到搵唔到支援哩個型號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢支持intel個512gb版 但我搵唔到我個256gb版係榜上有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad94f427b8e7f7d5dc10d9364a2f33abcd72e25","tid":252180,"uid":7992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"同一塊板 用緊960evo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42a46b915ef69c677152069a2ab14af6b4a6ea6","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同一塊板 用緊960evo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴晚你推你隻960evo 我見成千一縮左沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟手揀左600p <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家似出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4da97d15c0e86fd2bde024511f2c31c2e2b64ba","tid":252180,"uid":115295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"正常應該找到，試下Update Bios。"},{"pid":"e02013348544d339222a88324989ab5c8d5d5712","tid":252180,"uid":7992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"早叫你上1700 <br />\n960veo快過600p兩條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己test read有29XX"},{"pid":"ebfd5db363a79e3c5a1e1ceccec94597d0f760d8","tid":252180,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"用緊600p冇事喎"},{"pid":"9b407690b683b5f5c46503cc519514bff40b0e93","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早叫你上1700 <br />\n960veo快過600p兩條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己test read有29XX</blockquote><br />\n明明咩都加少少 就係柒係ssd手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51957e7f0e214eed4bde9e62c149bd9f7ea7707","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊600p冇事喎</blockqu