l/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f53c480c5382a2eea44098dad5de77478a851c","tid":252180,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我果陣都係bios見唔到隻600p<br />\n裝完windows就見到</blockquote><br />\n我家下裝左win10係hhd到 都係見唔到ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎隻windows usb去用uefi boot入去<br />\n再指落隻ssd度裝"},{"pid":"2e9e9ea63a0e728e40290ac53cd28922510d6d52","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果陣都係bios見唔到隻600p<br />\n裝完windows就見到</blockquote><br />\n我家下裝左win10係hhd到 都係見唔到ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎隻windows usb去用uefi boot入去<br />\n再指落隻ssd度裝</blockquote><br />\n點樣先可以uefi boot<br />\n唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8770e74fb6c6baef38a80ca49e9792c10642303","tid":252180,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果陣都係bios見唔到隻600p<br />\n裝完windows就見到</blockquote><br />\n我家下裝左win10係hhd到 都係見唔到ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎隻windows usb去用uefi boot入去<br />\n再指落隻ssd度裝</blockquote><br />\n點樣先可以uefi boot<br />\n唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbios入面應該有一樣叫boot option之類既野<br />\n改佢做UEFI only<br />\n然後睇下bios見唔見到隻windows usb先<br />\n見到就將隻usb set做boot drive<br />\n然後淨係插usb同ssd去裝左windows先"},{"pid":"385b856ea9941b76989501c38af7d9d44b0f6e87","tid":252180,"uid":25845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"你用咗legacy mode裝?"},{"pid":"adda548bb60b749b38f536743d37b805b10cc7d6","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果陣都係bios見唔到隻600p<br />\n裝完windows就見到</blockquote><br />\n我家下裝左win10係hhd到 都係見唔到ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎隻windows usb去用uefi boot入去<br />\n再指落隻ssd度裝</blockquote><br />\n點樣先可以uefi boot<br />\n唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbios入面應該有一樣叫boot option之類既野<br />\n改佢做UEFI only<br />\n然後睇下bios見唔見到隻windows usb先<br />\n見到就將隻usb set做boot drive<br />\n然後淨係插usb同ssd去裝左windows先</blockquote><br />\n你係咪裝完windows10未裝底板driver就見到隻600p係我的電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係裝完windows再開機入bios先見到隻600p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba394d90872e28adec02b5f6a34eefe2e49324d","tid":252180,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:38:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果陣都係bios見唔到隻600p<br />\n裝完windows就見到</blockquote><br />\n我家下裝左win10係hhd到 都係見唔到ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎隻windows usb去用uefi boot入去<br />\n再指落隻ssd度裝</blockquote><br />\n點樣先可以uefi boot<br />\n唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbios入面應該有一樣叫boot option之類既野<br />\n改佢做UEFI only<br />\n然後睇下bios見唔見到隻windows usb先<br />\n見到就將隻usb set做boot drive<br />\n然後淨係插usb同ssd去裝左windows先</blockquote><br />\n你係咪裝完windows10未裝底板driver就見到隻600p係我的電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係裝完windows再開機入bios先見到隻600p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝完windows之後<br />\nbios度會見到隻ssd叫做咩UEFI boot device之類乜柒既<br />\nset做boot drive就ok"},{"pid":"63ace6bb562bccb9c6f6f760ddec928edd70d8c6","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果陣都係bios見唔到隻600p<br />\n裝完windows就見到</blockquote><br />\n我家下裝左win10係hhd到 都係見唔到ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎隻windows usb去用uefi boot入去<br />\n再指落隻ssd度裝</blockquote><br />\n點樣先可以uefi boot<br />\n唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbios入面應該有一樣叫boot option之類既野<br />\n改佢做UEFI only<br />\n然後睇下bios見唔見到隻windows usb先<br />\n見到就將隻usb set做boot drive<br />\n然後淨係插usb同ssd去裝左windows先</blockquote><br />\n你係咪裝完windows10未裝底板driver就見到隻600p係我的電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係裝完windows再開機入bios先見到隻600p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝完windows之後<br />\nbios度會見到隻ssd叫做咩UEFI boot device之類乜柒既<br />\nset做boot drive就ok</blockquote><br />\n我搞左一輪入win安裝介面搵唔到隻ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhhd有拔左<br />\n uefi boot device哩到都係搵唔到 或者係我唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131652b2236fde218fa2f5aac64b6437cfc0a9a8","tid":252180,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我家下裝左win10係hhd到 都係見唔到ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎隻windows usb去用uefi boot入去<br />\n再指落隻ssd度裝</blockquote><br />\n點樣先可以uefi boot<br />\n唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbios入面應該有一樣叫boot option之類既野<br />\n改佢做UEFI only<br />\n然後睇下bios見唔見到隻windows usb先<br />\n見到就將隻usb set做boot drive<br />\n然後淨係插usb同ssd去裝左windows先</blockquote><br />\n你係咪裝完windows10未裝底板driver就見到隻600p係我的電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係裝完windows再開機入bios先見到隻600p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝完windows之後<br />\nbios度會見到隻ssd叫做咩UEFI boot device之類乜柒既<br />\nset做boot drive就ok</blockquote><br />\n我搞左一輪入win安裝介面搵唔到隻ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhhd有拔左<br />\n uefi boot device哩到都係搵唔到 或者係我唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我已經諗定聽日去換過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正都會唔會比我換<br />\n有冇人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}